OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772817081
OL,3,CWoman stranded in Dubai amid conflict
OL,4,Clands back in UK in time for
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FA cancer patient from Plymouth says
OL,8,Fshe is relieved to have returned to
OL,9,Fthe UK for her chemotherapy treatment
OL,10,Fafter becoming stranded in Dubai with
OL,11,Fher family during the Middle East
OL,12,Fconflict.
OL,14,FLindsay Stone, 47, was on holiday with
OL,15,Fher family and husband, Paul, after
OL,16,Fbeing recently diagnosed with lung
OL,17,Fcancer. The family wanted to take her
OL,18,Fon a short break before beginning her
OL,19,Ftreatment back at home.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
