FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43202
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772817081
OL,3,CWoman stranded in Dubai amid conflict
OL,4,Clands back in UK in time for
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FLindsay had been due to fly home on
OL,8,FSunday, to get back in time for her
OL,9,Fappointment, but the flight was
OL,10,Fcancelled because of the US-Israeli
OL,11,Fstrikes on Iran and the retaliatory
OL,12,FIranian attacks that followed.
OL,14,FThe Stone family was one of thousands
OL,15,Fwho have been stranded in Dubai as
OL,16,Fairlines cancelled flights and
OL,17,Fairspace was shut down.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
