FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43203
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772817081
OL,3,CWoman stranded in Dubai amid conflict
OL,4,Clands back in UK in time for
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FShe told ITV News West Country that
OL,8,Fshe first learned of the unfolding
OL,9,Fsituation from friends who had texted
OL,10,Fher to check she was safe.
OL,12,F"I put the news on and I realised, and
OL,13,Fas I ran to the pool to tell my
OL,14,Fhusband, I saw a drone being
OL,15,Fintercepted.
OL,17,F"I was just hearing the booms and
OL,18,Falerts going off, it was really
OL,19,Fscary", she said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43204
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772817081
OL,3,CWoman stranded in Dubai amid conflict
OL,4,Clands back in UK in time for
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FThe family was forced to stay in their
OL,8,Fhotel for two days as explosions rang
OL,9,Fout across the city.
OL,11,F"Seeing the drone made it very real,
OL,12,Fyou could hear multiple explosions
OL,13,Fthrough the night", Lindsay said.
OL,15,F"We had the alert going off on our
OL,16,Fphones during the night. You read the
OL,17,Ftext and you're like, 'oh my god, this
OL,18,Fis real'. You're just stuck inside
OL,19,Fbecause you don't know what you're
OL,20,Fgoing to do."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43205
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772817081
OL,3,CWoman stranded in Dubai amid conflict
OL,4,Clands back in UK in time for
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FBy Monday afternoon, Lindsay said the
OL,8,Fsituation appeared to ease.
OL,10,F"It felt calm, there was no panic, no
OL,11,Fhysteria, but you don't know how it's
OL,12,Fgoing to escalate", she said.
OL,14,FThe couple had been due to fly home on
OL,15,FSunday, but were confident their
OL,16,Fflight would not go ahead after
OL,17,Fairspace was closed.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
