FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43206
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772817081
OL,3,CWoman stranded in Dubai amid conflict
OL,4,Clands back in UK in time for
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FTheir fears were confirmed when Virgin
OL,8,FAtlantic cancelled their booking,
OL,9,Fbefore sending a follow-up email
OL,10,Fsaying the flight would operate after
OL,11,Fall, only to cancel it again.
OL,13,F"We then got a phone call from Virgin
OL,14,Fand were given a flight out on
OL,15,FWednesday," Paul said.
OL,17,F"Even when we were boarding, we
OL,18,Fcouldn't believe it. Once we were in
OL,19,Fthe air we were scared, we just
OL,20,Fthought, let's get out of here
OL,21,Fquickly."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43207
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772817081
OL,3,CWoman stranded in Dubai amid conflict
OL,4,Clands back in UK in time for
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FThey described Dubai International
OL,8,FAirport, normally one of the busiest
OL,9,Fin the world, as eery and deserted.
OL,11,FWatch as Lindsay and Paul walked
OL,12,Fthrough a deserted Dubai airport
OL,14,F"There was nobody there. It was a
OL,15,Fghost town. For the second busiest
OL,16,Fairport in the world, it was surreal.
OL,17,FNo stress, no delays, nobody was
OL,18,Fthere. Very weird, to say the least",
OL,19,FPaul said.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,433,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43208
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772817081
OL,3,CWoman stranded in Dubai amid conflict
OL,4,Clands back in UK in time for
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FThe couple eventually touched down
OL,8,Fsafely in the UK.
OL,10,F"We were so thankful to touch down, it
OL,11,Fwas a huge weight lifted off our
OL,12,Fshoulders", Lindsay said.
OL,14,F"To be home knowing we can crack on
OL,15,Fwith Lindsay's chemo was a huge
OL,16,Frelief", Paul added.
OL,18,F"I feel awful for so many people who
OL,19,Fare still stuck. They don't know when
OL,20,Fthey'll get back", Lindsay continued.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
