CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F432A1772817081
OL,3,CWoman stranded in Dubai amid conflict
OL,4,Clands back in UK in time for
OL,5,Cchemotherapy
OL,7,FA limited number of flights have been
OL,8,Fable to depart the United Arab
OL,9,FEmirates as disruption across the
OL,10,FMiddle East continues, following the
OL,11,Flaunch of the joint US-Israeli
OL,12,Fmilitary operation against Iran.
OL,14,FMore than 140,000 Britons have
OL,15,Fregistered their presence in the
OL,16,FMiddle East with the Foreign Office
OL,17,Fand 4,000 have returned home.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
